@node "NcodeRtech" "NcodeR - Caratteristiche tecniche"

NcodeR - The Amiga MP3 Encoder
==============================


Features
--------
Encoder features:
- very high-speed high-fidelity MP3 encoder
- WAVE, AIFF and MAUD sample input formats
- 32, 44.1 and 48 kHz Samplingrate
- full Nyquist bandwidth (16, 22.05 and 24 kHz)
- Mono, Stereo and MS-Stereo supported
- "Maximize" option to amplify weak signals

GUI features:
- user-friendly graphical interface
- two GUI versions
- "Skin"-Support, fully customizable
- can automatically process an unlimited number of files
- progress bar indicators
- user can abort at any time
- runs on any AGA/CyberGfx/Picasso96 Workbench
- supports all depths up to 24 bit using V43 picture.datatype



Requirements
------------
Minimum requirements:
68020 CPU
AmigaOS 3.x
4MB free RAM
datatypes.library
gtlayout.library

Optimal requirements:
PowerPC 604e CPU
picture.datatype V43+

